o-es-maradona-mundial-brasil-2014/14247923 |date=20140810150901 }} Futbol Red 2014 7 14</ref><ref name="iptv">[http://www.iptv-news.com/2014/07/world-cup-final-breaks-records-worldwide-for-tv-broadcasters/ "World Cup final breaks records worldwide for TV broadcasters"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.iptv-news.com/2014/07/world-cup-final-breaks-records-worldwide-for-tv-broadcasters/ |date=20140812100917 }} Iptv-news.com 2014 7 14</ref>。

